Revision history for Perl extension Tk::QuickForm.

0.08  Sat Feb 08 2025
	- Added option -colorhistoryfile.
	- Fixed using a single color picker for all color types.
	- Fixed POD errors

0.07  Sat Jan 18 2025
	- Added options -enables and -disables to the boolean and radio types.
	- Updated and revised documentation.

0.06  Sun Dec 15 2024
	- Changed bug tracker
	- Added switch '*frame'
	- File dialogs are done with Tk::FilePicker.

0.05  Tue Sep 10 2024
	All color types now use one popcolor widget

0.04  Sun Aug 20 2023
	Updated dependancies.
	Made method createForm return the notebook, if any;

0.03  Sat Jul 01 2023
	Fixed bug with loading item classes.

0.02  Wed Jum 28 2023
	Increased delay with testing to 1000 ms. This prevents tests failing on slow machines.

0.01  Sun Jun 25 2023
	Initial release
